title: Kwality
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family-run place serving Indian food and Thai food. Extensive menu with veggie choices, such as dahl, navratan korma, vegetable curries, Indian bread, several rice dishes plus Thai vegetable curry and spring rolls. Cooked to order. Access is off a side street with very steep stairs to the first floor. NOTE: please send the correct map coordinates to happycow!
